h2.fontface= title

p KDict is designed to be an community-based dictionary. Anyone is free to improve the dictionary by adding new definitions or modifying existing ones.

p If you are learning Korean, adding example sentence to entries when you look them up is a great way to remember new vocabulary.

h3.fontface Flagged Entries

p
  | There are a number of entries that have been detected as requiring editing or confirmation. Please help by viewing the list of
  a(href='/contribute/flagged') flagged entries

h3.fontface How?

p
  | In order to edit the dictionary, first
  a(href='/signup') sign up
  |  and log in to your account. From there you are able to edit dictionary metadata.

p Your changes will be made immediately, and added to a log of all the changes made to that entry.




